tatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217680/extras/0a6ab1bf71f222ea10f413cad1a116d0.webm?t=1689631780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217680/extras/0a6ab1bf71f222ea10f413cad1a116d0.mp4?t=1689631780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In Story Mode the game’s narrative unfolds as you traverse through hand-crafted levels packed with platforming action. You’ll battle bosses, make friends and enemies, and discover the grim truths of the 23rd century.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217680/extras/f780dae2138608b0fc2ab04b32df54fd.poster.avif?t=1689631780\" width=610 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217680/extras/f780dae2138608b0fc2ab04b32df54fd.webm?t=1689631780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217680/extras/f780dae2138608b0fc2ab04b32df54fd.mp4?t=1689631780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217680/extras/570e57391ce40fe77a776286ee68e0fb.webp?t=1689631780\" width=132 height=14 /></span><br>In the Roguelike ARCADE MODE you’ll battle hordes of foes in randomized arenas and compete on global leaderboards. Climb fences, mantle ledges, hang from bars, and leap from walls as you outmaneuver KOPs in search of upgrades and allies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217680/extras/c2fd91d403a2ce553e897243737a2122.poster.avif?t=1689631780\" width=608 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217680/extras/c2fd91d4